Files obtained from: http://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/Human+Activity+Recognition+Using+Smartphones
Files used: https://d396qusza40orc.cloudfront.net/getdata%2Fprojectfiles%2FUCI%20HAR%20Dataset.zip

Input File Info:
  activity_labels ~ titles for activities (see y below)
  features ~ titles for measured values (see x below)
  subject_test ~ ID # for subject test
  X_test ~ numeric data for test values [mean, std dev. etc.]
  y_test ~ ID # for activity test
  subject_train ~ ID # for subject train
  X_train ~ numeric data for train values [mean, std dev. etc.]
  y_train ~ ID # for activity train
Output File Info:
  Take measured values for mean and std dev. of each test and train session
  "Merge" all input files into cohesive table
  Tidied data
  Take mean of each measured group of measured means and std dev.
  Output as "tidy_data.txt"
